Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:36.24,Copy of Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,"Graduation"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Simon, congratulations \Non successfully
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndestroying the enemy base on RA221.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, that was splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally managed to land a blow\Nagainst the Wulgaru army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's hope yet that we can change\Nthe tide of this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, the Wulgaru \Nhas taken us lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that strike will serve as an excuse\Nto launch a massive attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must prepare for the \NWulgaru's counter-attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have already confirmed signs\Nof enemy movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are speaking out \Nof line, Deputy Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after this, I imagine \Nthe MJP will be back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on track, training pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they pump out more \Nexcellent students,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwe might actually win this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to increase the AHSMB \Nunit's production speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, that was a pretty \Nhard fight back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso maintenance has been killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Rhinos are just prototypes\Nfor your AHSMBs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way you fought with them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should be able \Nto show us up easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've just gotta get a \Ngrasp on your units first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our DNA has been programmed \Ninto our units,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhich makes piloting them relatively easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't rely too heavily on\Nyour machine's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one side relies too heavily on the other,\Nthe relationship is screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did ya need somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any porn on hand\Nif that's what ya want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received orders to return\Nto the academy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say "Goodbye" first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure we'll run into\Neach other again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the enemy \Nis already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Before I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This contains the data \Nfrom our last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI had it stored on my Rhinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our duties is to collect combat data\Nfor future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, we'll be headin' \Nback to the frontlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Data from the Rhinos units, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as the bigwigs are concerned,\Nall of us are just data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Doberman going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the frontlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're not sure why ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still lacking where it counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes you the Fail Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That last strike only worked because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthose other pilots were there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try not to make the \Nrest of us look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place never changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. It's kinda relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't relaxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we're working our butts off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor Suzukaze is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now if you'll pardon me, Team Fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she do that on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seriously thought \Nthat was our team name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does graduating entail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it means you have \Ncompleted your training
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and will officially enter the GDF army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The five of you will \Nbe graduating early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, I will be \Ntransferring with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the captain of the Godinion:\Nyour superior commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pack your belongings in your dorm rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will return to Star Rose tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and remain on standby \Nuntil tomorrow's mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,What Life Brought You
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they're rushing \Nus through graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that means, "From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can throw you into as many \Nbattles as we want!" huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to miss this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never dreamed I'd feel this way\Nwhen I first came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were practically \Nthrown into the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy was I shocked when I found out\Nwe were on the same team...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the next team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshikazu Asagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ataru Suruga,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izuru Hitachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei Kugimiya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Tamaki Irie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is younger than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you have any questions,\Nplease feel free to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Suruga,\Ndidn't you start out pretty quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea what to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our memories had just been wiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from class and the weather,\Nthere was nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo, class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Rabbits, you have excellent\Noffensive capabilities and mobility,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're getting E's in cooperation,\Nconcentration and operational stability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperation is an outright E-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd give her a fairly \Nlarge cup size...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An F would have been even better yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E is the lowest grade you can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some odd reason, everyone\Nstarted to open up after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All thanks to me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel empty now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I take this with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, didn't it belong to whoever\Nstayed here before us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tattered mess, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first manga I ever read.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,NEW\NSERIALIZATION!\NBUDDY SPIRITS 3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a load off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice knowing that we don't have\Nto come back here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet no one dreamed we'd be piloting\Nthe high-tech AHSMB units
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and graduating ahead of everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in their wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna cry by yourself, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to draw one last sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.80,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,FAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I never could \Nget this to come off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to clean out our desks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,How to Get a Wonderful Girlfriend\NLearn how girls think!\NWays for 'meh' guys\Nto find romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a magazine for guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DANCING CAKES\NMake dough for popular cakes,\Nsimple baked sweets that make your mouth dance, \Nand French recipes you've always dreamt of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, what were you \Ntwo doing during class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder we were called the Fail Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's seriously no wonder at all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you went!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi was wanting to fly one last lap\Naround the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your AHSMBs are currently being\Ntransported to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First Lt. Shirato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. The meeting just ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the economic powers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are squabbling over the \NAHSMB technology and units.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After fighting a losing war for so long,\Nwe had our first victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for the MJP\Nand the AHSMBs to garner attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:13:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they don't care about \Nfighting the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each country merely wants to\Nstand above the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting the Wulgaru isn't easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Earth politics are no \Nlaughing matter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so desperate for the technology
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that some are asking to sponsor\NGurantseere Cosmopolitan Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others are trying to \Nvolunteer new students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this fall outside \Nof your jurisdiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but with Commander Simon away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he visiting the academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! They are already packed.\NI believe they could leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it is still too soon for them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto become official members of the army...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have not fully \Nmastered their AHSMBs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus they still seem uncertain\Nabout the JURIA-SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to their innate personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki Irie and Ataru \NSuruga are adjusting to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the SYSTEM relatively well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Asagi and Kugimiya both
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndeteriorate and freeze on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times, Izuru Hitachi displays\Nbursts of power, but not reliably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is nothing left\Nfor you to teach them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine the JURIA-SYSTEM\Ncan only be mastered on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It requires situations where they\Nput their very lives on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see to tomorrow's preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AHSMB?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Are they real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nothing like our practice units.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck do we have to do\Na demonstration?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hardly something \Nto stress out over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're stressed BECAUSE \Nit's a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be scarier than a real battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we seriously have to \Ngo through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I explained yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NBlue 1 and Red 5 will perform linkages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold 4 will fire while under 1G.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be using live ammo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so bear in mind the \Ngravity, wind, humidity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand air density while calculating your trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purple 2 will issue orders and Rose 3\Nwill offer aerial support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That comprises this demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing I suck at...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You failed once in front of\Nthe entire universe, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you get to show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I get to do is shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm issuing orders from THERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be the most \Nembarrassing job...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Rabbits will hereby offer you\Na demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected a mission like this\Nbefore graduation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great chance to rid ourselves\Nof the name "Fail Five".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, you're planning to become\Nan instant school hero, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is a great \Nopportunity, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming we don't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue 1, Gold 4, Red 5, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue 1, Red 5, linkage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose 3, blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki, you went lower\Nthan you were supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold 4, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that applause for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all for their demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be the same without you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we'll be hitting\Nthe frontlines soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! Let's meet up again \Nsometime, Fail Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduates, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come receive your medal \Nof rank, Tamaki Irie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei Kugimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshikazu Asagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a doozy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking, Asagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll regret it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that gave you three \Nholes in your tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asagi hogged all of the attention\Nback there, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the type of attention I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never come back \Nhere again, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda... sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever our team is,\Nthat will be where our home is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's strive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to do our best as Team Fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not our team name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stoopy-poopy-doopy head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
